EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. GPS JAMMING EXERCISES 1000Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   23 THRU 29 SEP IN AREA WITHIN 90 MILES OF
   57-30N 010-45W. VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER
   AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL
   ON VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 292000Z SEP 19.
